                Maris Casiti <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>rum</ex></expan> L <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> XXX ala Part<expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>o</abbr><ex>rum</ex></expan> et <lb n="3"/>Araborum turma <lb n="4"/>Variagnis Masicates <lb n="5"/>frater et Tigranus <lb n="6"/>posierunt <note>sic</note>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes reitender Bogenschütze mit Pferdeführer. (B): Boppert: Z. 4: Vartagnis.</p>
            </div>
